quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  61,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  61,1,jo cheez asmano mein hai aur zameen mein hai sab khuda ki tanzih (tasbeh )karti hai aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  61,2,momino! tum aisi baatein kyun kaha karte ho jokiya nahi karte
  61,3,khuda is baat se sakht bezaar hai ke aisi baat kaho jo karo nahi
  61,4,jo log khuda ki raah mein ( aisay tor par ) paray jama kar lartay ke goya seesa pilayi deewar hain woh be shak mehboob kardgaaar hain
  61,5,aur woh waqt yaad karne ke Laiq hai jab moose ne apni qoum se kaha ke ae qoum! tum mujhe kyun aeza dete ho halaank tum jantay ho ke mein tumahray paas khuda ka bheja howa aaya hon. to jab un logon ne kaj rawi ki khuda ne bhi un ke dil tirhhe kardiye. aur khuda na farmanoon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  61,6,aur ( woh waqt bhi yaad karo ) jab maryam ke betay eesa ne kaha ke ae bani Israel mein tumahray paas khuda ka bheja howa aaya hon ( aur ) jo ( kitaab ) mujh se pehlay aa chuki hai ( yani ) torat is ki tasdeeq karta hon aur aik paighambar jo mere baad ayen ge jin ka naam Ahmed Sallallahu alaihi wasallam) hoga un ki basharat sunataa hon. ( phir ) jab woh un logon ke paas khuli nishanain le kar aeye to kehnay lagey ke yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai
  61,7,aur is se zalim kon ke bulaya to jaye islam ki taraf aur woh khuda par jhoot bohtan bandhay. aur khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
  61,8,yeh chahtay hain ke khuda ke ( chairag ) ki roshni ko munh se ( phoonk maar kar ) bujha den. halaank khuda apni roshni ko poora karkay rahay ga khuwa kafir nakhush hi hon
  61,9,wohi to hai jis ne apne paighambar ko hadaayat aur deen haq day kar bheja taakay usay aur sab deeno par ghalib kere khuwa mushrikon ko bura hi lagey
  61,10,momino! mein tum ko aisi tijarat batau jo tumhe azaab alim se mukhlasi day
  61,11,( woh yeh ke ) khuda par aur is ke Rasool Sallallahu alaihiwasallam) par imaan lao aur khuda ki raah mein apne maal aur jaan se jehaad karo. agar samjhoo to yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai
  61,12,woh tumahray gunah bakhash day ga aur tum ko baghaye jannat mein jin mein nehrain beh rahen hain aur pakeeza makanaat mein jo bahisht haae javedani mein ( tayyar ) hain daakhil kere ga. yeh barri kamyabi hai
  61,13,aur aik aur cheez jis ko tum bohat chahtay ho ( yani tumhe ) khuda ki taraf se madad ( naseeb hogi ) aur fatah anqareeb hogi aur mominoun ko ( is ki ) khushkhabri suna do
  61,14,momino! khuda ke madadgaar ban jao jaisay eesa Ibn maryam ne hawarion se kaha ke bhala kon hain jo khuda ki taraf ( bulanay mein ) mere madadgaar hon. hawarion ne kaha ke hum khuda ke madadgaar hain. to bani Israel mein se aik giroh to imaan le aaya aur aik giroh kafir raha. aakhir- ul amr hum ne imaan laane walon ko un ke dushmanon ke muqablay mein madad di aur woh ghalib hogaye
